Mu [[Rwanda]] munzizi ibiyaga hakunze kuboneka icyatsi kitwa "AMAREBE' ni ikimera kimera mu mazi ibibabi byacyo bikazamuka ejuru ni indabyo siza nk'idoma .

Mu karere ka Bugesera mu kiyaga cyohoha hagaragayemo icyi cyatsi kibi ku rusobe ry'ibinyabuzima biba mu mazi.

Hatangijwe umushinga wo kurandura icyo cyatsi cy' amarebe mu karere ka Bugesera mu kurengera ibidukikije<ref>Bugesera: Umushinga wo gukura amarebe mu Kiyaga cya Cyohoha ya ruguru umaze gukura bamwe mu bukene - Kigali Today</ref>.

== Ibibi by'amarebe . ==
Amarebe n'umwanzi w'urusobe rw'ibinyabuzima mu biyaga, imigezi n'inzuzi.

Amarebe yororoka vuba akareremba heruru y'amazi agafunga imiyoboro y'amazi yo kuhira urusobe rw'ibimyabuzima  ruri mu mazi rukazahara ,umusaruro w'amafi ukagabanuka n'amato ntagenda neza nk'uko bikwiye .

Uko amarebe agenda agwira mu kiyaga byangiza ikiyaga kuko amarebe agenda aba meshi bigabanya ubwiza bw'amazi ku binyabuzima buri mu mazi bimwe bikanapfa .

Amarebe nanone icyatsi kibi kica urusobe rw'ibimera gisanga mu mazi .

== Igisubizo cyabonetse mu kubyaza umusaruro amarebe . ==
Mu murenge wa Gashora hari itsinda rya abagore ribyaza  amarebe akamaro hakorwamo bimwe mu bikoresho byifashishwa ;harimo inkweto ,ibikapu ,inofero n'ibindi mu rwego rwo kurengera ibidukikije n'urusobe rw'ibinyabuzima <ref>Gashora: Amarebe yari ikibazo none yabaye igisubizo - Kigali Today</ref>.

